These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-1::.
There 5 different types of food: nectarine, tomato, grapes, watermelon, apple
The people have 5 different hobbies: dancing, chess, video-games, skydiving, traveling
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: salsa, rock, r&b, ambient, gospel
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, december, april, october, may
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person eating tomato##1
 3. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 4. the person eating grapes is the person eating grapes##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 6. the person eating apple is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
 7. the fan salsa is on the left of the fan r&b##1
 8. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the person eating watermelon is on the far right##1
10. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
11. the person eating apple is between the fan rock and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
12. the fan ambient is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
13. the fan gospel is on the right of the person eating grapes##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |    5     |
| Food      | nectarine        | tomato | apple     | grapes   | watermelon |
| Hobby   | video-games     | chess      | skydiving | traveling   | dancing    |
| Music-Genre   | ambient  | rock     | salsa | r&b | gospel  |
| Birthday           | december | april      | may     | october   | february     |

