.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-2::.
City: boston, paris, liverpool, nizza, san-francisco
House: modern, art-deco, wooden, tower, craftsman
The people have 5 different jobs:  videographer, musician, freelancer, chef, dancer
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: volleyball, basketball, surfing, parkour, rugby
 1. the person who's sport is rugby is in the middle##1
 2. the craftsman house is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 3. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the musician##1
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is between the videographer and the craftsman house##2
 6. the person who's sport is parkour is the person traveling to paris##1
 7. the modern house is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 8. the freelancer is the tower house##1
 9. the freelancer is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1
10. the wooden house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
11. the freelancer is the person traveling to liverpool##1
12. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| City         | nizza | boston | san-francisco    | paris  | liverpool    |
| House   | craftsman    | art-deco       | wooden      | modern | tower        |
| Job   | dancer   | musician     | videographer    | chef  | freelancer     |
| Sport     | surfing    | basketball | rugby | parkour | volleyball |

