 2. the person watching romance movies is on the far left##1
 3. the person playing mah-jongg is the person watching epic movies##1
 4. the person playing domino is between the person drinking coffee and the dunhill-smoker##2
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
