 4. the person playing go is the person drinking coffee##1
 5. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
 6. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 7. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the scientist##1
 8. the person playing billiard is the person who growsmarigold##1
 9. the project-manager is on the far left##1
10. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
11. the person who growsrose is between the person playing billiard and the project-manager##2
12. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
13. the analyst is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
