.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-17::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, bluemaster, havana, fonseca, cain
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: april, january, march, june, november
House: colonial, wooden, cape-cod, victorian, craftsman
There are 5 different nationalities: malaysian, turkish, american, german, mexican
 1. the craftsman house is between the turkish and the wooden house##2
 2. the cape-cod house is on the left of the victorian house##1
 3. the bluemaster-smoker is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 4. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the craftsman house##1
 5. the turkish is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the turkish##1
 7. the malaysian is on the right of the mexican##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
10. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1
11. the american is between the cape-cod house and the person who's birthday is in march##2
12. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
13. the havana-smoker is on the left of the fonseca-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4     |     5      |
| Cigar    | havana       | fonseca    | cain | bluemaster  | bolivar        |
| Birthday       | november | april | march  | june | january    |
| House       | cape-cod        | victorian   | wooden  | craftsman   | colonial |
| Nationality   | german       | american      | mexican      | malaysian | turkish  |

