 1. the person traveling to london is on the left of the french##1
 2. the person who likes brown is between the polish and the person who likes fuchsia##2
 3. the person who growsamaryllis is the person who likes brown##1
 4. the chinese is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 5. the japanese is in the middle##1
 6. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person who likes blue and the person traveling to hamburg##2
 7. the person traveling to rome is the person who growslily##1
 8. the person who growsaconite is the person traveling to london##1
 9. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person who likes blue##1
10. the person who likes coral is on the right of the polish##1
11. the person who likes fuchsia is the french##1
12. the australian is on the far left##1
13. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1

