 3. the ranch-style house is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person who growsmarigold is between the fan punk and the person who growsdaisy##2
 6. the fan punk is on the far left##1
 7. the craftsman house is between the person watching sports movies and the ranch-style house##2
 8. the futuristic house is between the art-deco house and the farmhouse house##2
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
10. the farmhouse house is on the right of the fan techno##1

