.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-2-20::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, blend, ritmeester, taxi-climbing, dannemann
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: begonia, lily, bellflower, aconite, amaryllis
The people use 5 different means of transport: jet-ski, bus, snowmobile, helicopter, taxi
There 5 different types of food: nectarine, cranberry, grapes, mango, artichoke
 1. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
 2. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person eating mango and the person driving the taxi##2
 3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 4. the person who growsamaryllis is the person driving the jet-ski##1
 5. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person eating artichoke and the person driving the snowmobile##2
 6. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 7. the person who growsbellflower is the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the taxi-climbing-smoker is the person driving the bus##1
 9. the person eating nectarine is the person driving the bus##1
10. the taxi-climbing-smoker is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
11. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
12. the person who growslily is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |      4       |       5       |
| Cigar         | ritmeester    | dannemann  | blend  | prince      | taxi-climbing |
| Flower   | lily    | amaryllis   | aconite | bellflower | begonia   |
| Transport   | snowmobile | jet-ski    | taxi    | helicopter       | bus         |
| Food   | mango  | cranberry | artichoke    | grapes     | nectarine      |

 